<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1873-11-14T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1873-11-14T00:00:00-05:00" n="610" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d610">
                            <head>No. 608.<lb/><hi rend="italic">General <persName type="from">Sickles</persName> to Mr. <persName type="to">Fish</persName>.</hi></head>
                            <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                            <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Madrid</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1873-11-14"><hi rend="italic">November</hi> 14,
                                        1873</date>.</dateline></opener>
                            <p>Your cable of 12th, beginning “An official bulletin,” received early
                                same day. The other was delivered this morning. Yours of this date
                                received at 10.30 to-night.</p>
                            <closer><signed>SICKLES.</signed></closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>